    {
        "url": "/quotes/derek_cianfrance_784847",
        "quote": "I think people need fantasy, but I think they also need to know that they're not being lied to. I think sometimes the fantasy can betray people and become more difficult for people's lives than just truth. I can't stand delusion. Delusion makes me sick.",
