    {
        "url": "/quotes/derek_cianfrance_784796",
        "quote": "There's this thing in Hollywood about the sympathetic character and likability. I've never understood that because the people I love most in my life are not likable all the time. My wife is not always likable. I'm certainly not always likable. My dad is not always likable. We're human beings.",
