    {
        "url": "/quotes/derek_cianfrance_784841",
        "quote": "I shot 'Blue Valentine' on 16mm for the past, and for the present on the Red Camera. I feel that both formats are valid. The stories should dictate the format we shoot on. Filmmakers should have a choice.",
